• Apps

    • Binance Ninja: An app that notifies you about orders happening on Binance P2P trades.
    • CryptoNiffler : A cryptocurrency arbitrage and news app.

  • Plugins

    • Dimenify : An Android Studio plugin to manage auto scaling dimensions across different density buckets.
    • Alphabet: An Android Studio plugin that helps you pick color alphas more intutively.

  • Widgets

    • CenterLock Recyclerview: An android listener that snaps items to center. This is now superseded by SnapHelper.
